The dragon bot was flying over the battle scene when he sensed someone 
new he didnt know. He felt this bot to be confusing... He could not 
really determine who she was, so he decided to go and meet her.

AzureBlade: Greetings, I am AzureBlade. Tell me, who are you?

--- In nbwrpg@y..., logomorph@h... wrote:
> DarkMouse::
> 
> She walked and dragged her tail in the dirt as she walked.  She 
moved 
> closer to the maximal city.  She was now only a quarter of a mile 
> from the outside walls.  She wondered how long untill the cannons 
> would come down on her. Little did she know the maximal chip inside 
> her totally disguised her predacon signature. So when the automated 
> systems tracked her, they would only see a maximal and not a 
predacon.
> 
> (OK, I'll need someone in the maximal city who just might be 
watching 
> the scanners or watching the perimeter to at least pick up the 
> maximal signal and attempt to talk to her. Thank you. )
